react hooks are inbuilt functions provided by react that allows fucntional compo to use state and lifecycle feature.
before hooks class component lifecycle methods were used to maintain state in react

useState - state
useEffect - side effect
useContext - context
useReducer - complex state
useCallback - memoization
useMemo - performance
useRef  - refs
useLayouteffect - synchronous side effects

Always Start with "use":

Hooks Should Be Called at the Top Level: 

Hooks Should Be Called in the Same Order:

Avoid Using Hooks Inside Loops or Nested Functions: